document_data.name: Wanese
document_data.mainbody: The '''Wanese''' were a [[human]] ethnicity who lived on the islands of [[Wa]] in [[Kara-Tur]]. They were similar to the [[Kozakuran]] people.{{Cite dragon/Speaking in Tongues|26}}<ref>{{Cite dragon/315/Kara-Tur: Ancestor Feats and Martial Arts Styles|63-64}}
